{"article_id":"JkcieaJpuAj6WtgO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump did not press Ukraine ' s president for an investigation of Democratic front-runner Joseph R. Biden and his son in return for a promise of military aid ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"according to a transcript of their July phone call","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"released Wednesday by the Justice Department .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"In the July 25 call , Mr. Trump did raise the Bidens with Ukraine President Volodymyr Zelensky ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"the transcript shows .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"It involved the question","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"of whether Mr. Biden had pressured Ukraine to stop an investigation in 2016 of a Ukrainian gas company","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"that paid Hunter Biden $ 3 million .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"\" There ' s a lot of talk about Biden ' s son ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"that Biden stopped the prosecution","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"and a lot of people want to find out about that ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"so whatever you can do with the Attorney General","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"[ William P. Barr ]","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"would be great , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Mr. Trump said on the call .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" Biden went around bragging","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"that he stopped the prosecution","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"so if you can look into it ...","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"It sounds horrible to me . \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Zelensky responded","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that the country ' s new prosecutor would be loyal to him .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"\" He or she will look into the situation , specifically to the company","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that you mentioned in this issue , \"","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"he pledged to Mr. Trump .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"They also talked about the U.S. cybersecurity firm CrowdStrike and the controversy over the Democratic National Committee servers","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"hacked in 2016 .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"But there is no \" quid pro quo \" evident in the written account of the phone conversation .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"House Democrats announced a formal impeachment inquiry Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"based on their suspicions","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that Mr. Trump tried to pressure the Ukrainian leader into investigating the Bidens","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"by withholding $ 391 million in military aid last summer .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Trump had committed a \" betrayal \" of the Constitution .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"The president and his team say","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Biden ' s son , Hunter , should be investigated","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"for receiving $ 3 million from a Ukrainian energy company","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"while his father was serving as vice president .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"But the transcript ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"compiled from notes","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"taken by White House aides during the phone call ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"shows","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that Mr. Trump did not link the military aid to any promise from Ukraine for an investigation of his main Democratic rival .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"While there ' s no overt link to U.S. military aid ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Trump does ask Mr. Zelensky for a \" favor \"","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"immediately after reminding the Ukrainian leader","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that the U.S. has spent \" a lot of effort and a lot of time \" on Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"\" I would like you to do us a favor though","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"because our country has been through a lot","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and Ukraine knows a lot about it , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Trump said on the call .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" I would like you to find out what happened with this whole situation with Ukraine ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"they say","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Crowdstrike ...","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"I guess","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"you have one of your wealthy people...","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"The [ DNC ]","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"server ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"they say","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Ukraine has it .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"There are a lot of things","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that went on the whole situation ...","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"I would like to have the Attorney General","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"[ Mr. Barr ]","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"call you or your people","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"and I would like you to get to the bottom of it . \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"CrowdStrike was hired by the DNC initially","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to examine its servers in the Russian hacking affair .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"The DNC never turned over the servers to the FBI .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The president also mentions the just-completed investigation of special counsel Robert Mueller over unfounded allegations of Russian collusion with the Trump campaign .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Trump and his lawyer , Rudolph Giuliani , believe","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"the so-called \" witch hunt \" investigation had its origins in Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"\" They say","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"a lot of it started with Ukraine , \"","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Mr. Trump told Mr. Zelensky .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" Whatever you can do , it ' s very important that you do it","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"if that ' s possible . \"","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"the U.S. is helping Ukraine \" much more","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"than the European countries are doing ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and they should be helping you more","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"than they are . \"","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"\" Germany does almost nothing for you , \"","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"\" The United States has been very , very good to Ukraine .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"I wouldn ' t say","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that it ' s reciprocal necessarily","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"because things are happening","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that are not good ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but the United States has been very , very good to Ukraine . \"","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Zelensky replied ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"\" You are absolutely right .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"I ' m very grateful to you for that","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"because the United States is doing quite a lot for Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Much more than the European Union especially ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"when we are talking about sanctions against the Russian Federation . \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Democrats said","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"the transcript shows","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"the president ' s actions were worse","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"than they expected .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Republicans said","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"it proves","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"the president did nothing wrong .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , South Carolina Republican , said","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"\" I don ' t mind \"","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"that Mr. Trump raised the Bidens during the call .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"it ' s very appropriate for the president of the United States to suggest","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"[ to Ukraine ]","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"that you ' ve got a corruption problem , \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Graham told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"\" Did the president of the United States suggest to the Ukraine ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"' I will withhold money","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"unless you go after my political rival ' ?","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"The answer is absolutely not .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"That ' s why I wanted the phone call to be released . \"","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Mr. Graham said","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Mr. Biden ' s son \" was receiving money from the Ukraine ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"was on the board of a company","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that was the subject of an investigation . \"","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"\" If you don ' t see that conflict ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"you ' re blind , \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Mr. Trump said Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"the transcript would show","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"that Democrats owe him an apology","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"for rushing to an impeachment inquiry","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"without the facts .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"\" Will the Democrats apologize","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"after seeing what was said on the call with the Ukrainian President ? \"","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"The president tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"\" They should ,","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"a perfect call","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"- got them by surprise ! \"","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Mr. Trump is scheduled to meet with Mr. Zelensky later Wednesday at the United Nations in New York .","depth":4},{"id":134,"text":"White House deputy press secretary Hogan Gidley said","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"the transcript shows","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"\" the president has done nothing wrong here . \"","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"\" There is no quid pro quo","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"and there is no pressure , \"","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"Mr. Gidley said on Fox News .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"\" As the president has said ,","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"it was pitch-perfect .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"The Democrats are already calling for impeachment","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"when they didn ' t have the facts in the first place .","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"Evidence doesn ' t matter to Democrats at all . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":289,"left":239,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":181,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":181,"left":171,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":170,"right":26,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":147,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":146,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":167,"right":168,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":151,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":148,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":5,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":157,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":153,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":154,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":160,"right":164,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":18,"relatio